author: slaws
msg: Re-enable 8002 by fixing up the error messages to match the latest runtime behaviour

author: scottbw
msg: Updated widgets to use the current localization model and removed dependencies on shared language helper and util JS in wookie-wrapper.js (see WOOKIE-97). This means that there are fewer objects in the global space - just the Widget object itself - and that wookie-wrapper.js is much smaller and loads faster.
